   <body>
      <p>In <ph href="../../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/>, all the error messages that are displayed in the UI are compiled in one place so that you can view and modify them based on the requirements. The <uicontrol>Error Message Configurator</uicontrol> form enables you to view and modify error messages in the UI by changing the sentence structure without changing the code.</p>
      <p>In the <uicontrol>ERROR MESSAGE CONFIGURATOR</uicontrol> list page, each error message displays the information to help you understand from which module these messages are generated and why these messages are generated.</p>
      <p>The following sections describe types of error messages, viewing error messages, and modifying error messages:</p>
